dcterms:description: PSYDIAL is the first Korean dialogue dataset focused on personality-based dialogues, curated using a novel end-to-end personality-based synthetic dialogue generation pipeline. It includes approximately 2900 machine-generated conversations primarily focusing on the Extraversion dimension of the Big Five personality model.
